2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses a fully convolutional network trained end-to-end with losses that exploit low-level and high-level image information. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses a neural network for the task of reflection separation. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image enhancement tasks. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image processing and enhancement.
